msgid ""
"Like :ref:`wait <class_Semaphore_method_wait>`, but won't block, so if "
"the value is zero, fails immediately and returns "
":ref:`@GlobalScope.ERR_BUSY <class_@GlobalScope_constant_ERR_BUSY>`. If "
"non-zero, it returns :ref:`@GlobalScope.OK "
"<class_@GlobalScope_constant_OK>` to report success."
msgstr ""

